As described above, in resins used in application fields of which highly-advanced optical properties are required, other than a fact that they have general optical properties, the control of specific wavelength dependency about birefringence that the birefringence of transmitted light becomes higher as the wavelength of the transmitted light becomes longer when a film is formed, and degree of the birefringence become great problems.
